####################
# DHCP server/client
####################

Start imunes:

# imunes DHCP.imn &
      Select Experiment -> Execute

Start dhcp server and setup clients:
# ./start_dhcp

Right-click on pc3 (to start xterm on that host)
Check IP address:
pc3# ifconfig -a

Release address:
pc3# dhclient -r

Request IP address:
pc# dhclient eth0
pc# ifconfig -a

To look at the traffic right-click on selected link.
After a few moments Ethereal will be started!

